{{Infobox political party |country= Egypt | name = 25-30 Alliance |native_name= تحالف 25-30 |logo= |leader= |ideology= |national= |position = |website= |foundation=20 July 2014<ref>{{cite news|url=http://almesryoon.com/السياسية/520739-اليوم-انطلاق-تحالف-25-30-لدعم-المستقلين-في-الانتخابات-البرلمانية-المقبلة|title=اليوم.. انطلاق تحالف "25-30" لدعم المستقلين في الانتخابات البرلمانية المقبلة اقرأ المقال الاصلى فى المصريون|work=Almesryoon|date=20 July 2014|accessdate=21 October 2014}}</ref> |seats1_title = [[House of Representatives (Egypt)|House of Representatives]] |seats1 = {{Composition bar|14|568}} }}
The '''25-30 Alliance''' is an alliance of independents that will run in the [[Egyptian parliamentary election, 2015|2015 Egyptian parliamentary election]].<ref name=aawsat21july>{{cite news|url=http://www.aawsat.net/2014/07/article55334523|title=Egypt: New independent alliance prepares to fight parliamentary elections|agency=Asharq Al-Awsat|date=21 July 2014|accessdate=21 July 2014}}</ref> The name of the alliance refers to the revolution that overthrew [[Hosni Mubarak]] on 25 January 2011 and the overthrow of [[Mohamed Morsi]] on 30 June 2013.<ref name=aawsat21july/> Members of the [[April 6 Youth Movement]] and [[Tamarod]] will join the alliance; the [[Free Egyptians Party]] might join as well.<ref name=aawsat21july/> The alliance has put in place quotas for women and youth on its [[electoral list]]s.<ref name=aawsat21july/> Abdel-Hakim Abdel Nasser started the alliance.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/News/6980/17/Political-jockeying.aspx|title=Political jockeying|agency=Al-Ahram Weekly|date=14 August 2014|accessdate=20 August 2014}}</ref> Members of the alliance will run for individual seats in the parliament.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www1.youm7.com/story/2014/9/29/%D8%AA%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%81_25_30__%D8%AA%D9%84%D9%82%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%A7_150_%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A9_%D8%B0%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8A%D8%A9_%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%B4%D8%AD%D9%8A%D9%86_%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%AA%D9%85%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%86_%D9%88%D9%86%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B3_%D8%B9%D9%84/1885647|title=تحالف 25/30: تلقينا 150 سيرة ذاتية لمرشحين محتملينوننافس على "الفردى"|agency=Youm7|date=29 September 2014|accessdate=29 September 2014}}</ref> The alliance has indicated that it is not part of the [[Reawakening of Egypt]] list.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.el-balad.com/1418111|title=تحالف "25- 30" ينفى وقف أنشطته الانتخابية.. ويؤكد: لن نؤيد قائمة صحوة|agency=El Balad|date=3 March 2015|accessdate=3 March 2015}}</ref>
