{{Infobox Government agency |agency_name = Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs of the People's Republic of China |nativename_a = {{nobold|{{lang|zh-hans|中华人民共和国农业农村部}}}} |nativename_r = {{small|''Zhōnghuá Rénmín Gònghéguó Nóngyè Nóngcūnbù}} |logo = |logo_width = |logo_caption = |seal = National Emblem of the People's Republic of China.svg |seal_width = 150px |seal_caption = [[Emblem of the People's Republic of China]] |formed = {{Start date|2018|03|19}} |preceding1 = |preceding2 = |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = {{PRC}} |headquarters = [[Beijing]] |employees = |budget = |minister1_name = [[Han Changfu]]<ref>{{cite news|author= |url = http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201803/19/WS5aaf1a7aa3106e7dcc1426fd.html |title=China's new cabinet members endorsed |newspaper=Chinadaily |date=2018-03-19 |language=}}</ref> |minister1_pfo = |parent_agency = [[State Council of the People's Republic of China|State Council]] |child1_agency = |child2_agency = |website = <!-- {{url| }} --> |footnotes = }}
The '''Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs''' ({{zh|s=中华人民共和国农业农村部|t=中華人民共和國農業農村部|p=Zhōnghuá Rénmín Gònghéguó Nóngyè Nóngcūnbù}}) is a [[Ministry (government department)|ministry]] of the [[government of the People's Republic of China]] which is responsible for [[agriculture]] and [[Rural area|rural affairs]] in the country. The ministry is headquartered in Beijing. It was formed on 19 March 2018 as a replacement for its predecessor, the [[Ministry of Agriculture of the People's Republic of China|Ministry of Agriculture]]. Some of its additional responsibilities come from the agricultural investment projects of the [[National Development and Reform Commission]], the [[Ministry of Finance of the People's Republic of China|Ministry of Finance]], the [[Ministry of Land and Resources of the People's Republic of China|Ministry of Land and Resources]], and the [[Ministry of Water Resources of the People's Republic of China|Ministry of Water Resources]].<ref>{{cite news|author=Yang Shisheng |url=http://www.chinatimes.cc/article/75367.html |script-title=zh:统筹20多个涉农资金的部门职能 农业农村部“财权”更大了 |newspaper=chinatimes |date=2018-03-16 |language=zh}}</ref>
==History== On March 19, 2018, the [[Government of the People's Republic of China]] announced that the Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Affairs has been created at the first session of the [[13th National People's Congress]]. That same day, [[Han Changfu]] was elected Minister of Agriculture and Rural Affairs<ref>{{cite news|author= |url=http://news.163.com/18/0319/10/DD8MHJTT0001875N.html#from=relevant |script-title=zh:全国人大经投票表决 决定韩长赋为农业农村部部长 |newspaper=163.com |date=2018-03-19 |language=zh}}</ref>
